<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="129" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="0.[1240,2119,692,882]" pageId="0" pageNumber="129">® Smallto medium-sized marsupals with mostly-naked tails, pointed snouts, prehensile hands and feet with five fingers on both and claws on hands, and opposable thumbs on hindfeet; some species with a pouch.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1240,2119,692,882]" box="[1240,1429,849,882]" pageId="0" pageNumber="129">
