.
</paragraph>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6685342" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6685342" box="[1240,1803,1086,1119]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6685342/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="129" startId="0.[1240,1252,1086,1119]" targetBox="[226,1171,695,1317]" targetPageId="0">
<paragraph blockId="0.[1240,2120,1086,1317]" box="[1240,1803,1086,1119]" pageId="0" pageNumber="129">* Nearctic and Neotropical Regions.</paragraph>
