<paragraph blockId="0.[1240,2120,1086,1317]" pageId="0" pageNumber="129">* Wide-ranging, virtually present in all vegetation formations and biomes of the Americas from 50° N to 48° S.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1240,2120,1086,1317]" box="[1240,1883,1208,1237]" pageId="0" pageNumber="129">* 18 genera, 103 species, at least 143 taxa.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1240,2120,1086,1317]" pageId="0" pageNumber="129">* 2 species Critically Endangered, 6 species Vulnerable;1 species Extinct since 1600.</paragraph>
